description: A Brazilian congressional panel recommends impeaching President Dilma Rousseff. The former leader, Luiz Inácio Lula da Silva, spoke in support of Ms. Rousseff.
title: President of Brazil May Face Impeachment
title_page: President of Brazil May Face Impeachment - Video - NYTimes.com
text: A Brazilian congressional panel recommends impeaching President Dilma Rousseff. The former leader, Luiz Inácio Lula da Silva, spoke in support of Ms. Rousseff.
